sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant Thread as Java Thread
    participant JVM as JVM Scheduler
    participant Monitor as Monitor/Lock

    App->>Thread: new Thread()
    Thread->>JVM: Thread in NEW state

    App->>Thread: thread.start()
    Thread->>JVM: Transition to RUNNABLE

    JVM->>Thread: Schedule for execution
    Thread->>JVM: Running (RUNNABLE)

    Note over Thread,JVM: May be preempted or waiting for resources

    Thread->>Monitor: Attempt to acquire lock
    alt Lock available
        Monitor-->>Thread: Acquired, continue RUNNABLE
    else Lock not available
        Monitor-->>Thread: BLOCKED
        JVM->>Thread: Wait for lock
        Monitor-->>Thread: Lock acquired, back to RUNNABLE
    end

    Thread->>JVM: wait(), join(), or park()
    JVM-->>Thread: WAITING or TIMED_WAITING

    App->>Thread: notify(), notifyAll(), or timeout expires
    JVM-->>Thread: Back to RUNNABLE

    Thread->>JVM: run() completes or uncaught exception
    JVM-->>Thread: TERMINATED
